import React, { useState } from 'react'
import { StyleSheet, Text, View } from 'react-native'
import Card from '../../../components/Card'
import { CardType, SubscriptionData } from '../../../components/types'
import {Surface} from 'react-native-paper'
import { Button } from 'react-native-elements'

const PaySubscribe = () => {
    const [subscribeData, setSubscribeData] = useState<SubscriptionData>()
    return (
        <View>
            <Card title="몇명이 사용하시나요" data={subscribeData} type={CardType.CHARGE}/>
            <Card title="결제주기를 선택해주세요" subtitle="멤버 1명 당 결제금액" data={subscribeData} type={CardType.CHARGERENDER}/>
            <Card title="총 결제하실 금액(부가세 포함)" subtitle="2021년 1월 1일 ~ 2022년 12월 31일" data={subscribeData} type={CardType.CHARGERENDER}/>
            <View style={{flexDirection:'row', justifyContent:'space-between'}}>
                <Surface style={styles.surface}>
                    <Button title = "수동결제" type="clear" />
                </Surface>
                <Surface style={styles.surface}>
                    <Button title = "자동결제" type="clear" />
                </Surface>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}

export default PaySubscribe

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    surface: {
        padding: 8,
        width: 260,
        height: 200,
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        elevation: 8,
      },
})
